WEBVTT

00:02.933 --> 00:05.268
Basically, the animal
nucleotides are taking over

00:05.270 --> 00:06.585
from the human ones.

00:06.587 --> 00:08.154
<i>And whatever it is...</i>

00:08.156 --> 00:09.572
it's changing.

00:09.574 --> 00:11.407
CATHERINE: <i>He's becoming</i>
<i>less human.</i>

00:11.409 --> 00:14.277
He says it's mutating;
becoming more animal.

00:14.279 --> 00:15.828
I should probably go.

00:17.114 --> 00:19.031
Heather, uh...
I need your keys.

00:19.033 --> 00:21.801
I need to go and find somebody.

